{"tid":2065246,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"退役美海軍陸戰隊成員間諜罪成 俄羅斯法院比原定輕判  判監十六年","createTime":"2020-06-15T12:00:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-15T12:22:16.000Z","uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b8081164177a083a84a32cba3e0727463df7aee1","tid":2065246,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T12:00:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=394539\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D394539&d=UliE8fwpyfwMZiesMcCM7hUxn6Ez5IAhGrAWUjzTwv4%3D&h=cce81ed7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D394539&h=72020654\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=394539</a><br />\n【Now新聞台】俄羅斯法院以間諜罪判處一名美國退役海軍陸戰隊成員監禁十六年。<br />\n<br />\n50歲的惠蘭擁有美國、英國、加拿大和愛爾蘭護照。前年年底，他在莫斯科一間酒店房間被俄羅斯聯邦安全局人員拘捕，指控他藏有的記憶體，儲存了機密資料，涉嫌做間諜。<br />\n<br />\n惠蘭否認控罪，聲稱是遭設局陷害，又解釋以為俄羅斯朋友給他的記憶體裏面只是度假相片。<br />\n<br />\n莫斯科市法院經過閉門聆訊後，判處惠蘭監禁十六年，比檢察官的求刑少了兩年。惠蘭的家人表示，律師會在十日內提出上訴。<br />\n<br />\n美國駐俄羅斯大使沙利文認為審訊不公平和不透明，控罪亦沒有足夠證據，認為判決會影響美俄關係。俄羅斯外交部表示，多次向美國提出交換囚犯，但都得不到回應。"},{"pid":"32cbeecd874bf6fa4559b5b78c058f322997ca0c","tid":2065246,"uid":52215,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T12:01:14.000Z","msg":"俄佬好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ac760e01ceddeaee152e6735a94ce0bbe9da645","tid":2065246,"uid":108467,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T12:01:38.000Z","msg":"沙田you五毛"},{"pid":"4afef8c5db3e7b851092955d295836330d132d8c","tid":2065246,"uid":51701,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1ac760e01ceddeaee152e6735a94ce0bbe9da645","tid":2065246,"uid":108467,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T12:01:38.000Z","msg":"沙田you五毛"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T12:03:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"ht